<item>
            <title>[LU-16901] Provide l_getidentity_nss identity provider</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16901</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;l_getidenity to fetch user&apos;s supplementary groups info from NIS, LDAP and/or any other services that NSS modules exist for.  Add lustre-only user/group configuration in plain files, keeping Lustre users and groups separate from Linux users/groups on Lustre server&apos;s machines for security reason&lt;/p&gt;</description>
